	<ofx:title lang="en">File Export</ofx:title>
	
	<ofx:paragraph lang="en">
		In some situations, the <text:emphasis bold="true">MEIS</text:emphasis> allows the user to export data into a file. Two different types are available, a file for <text:emphasis bold="true">Microsoft Excel</text:emphasis> or as PDF report.
        Therefore, you must simply click on the respective icon and your
		browser will most likely ask you to open or save (or choose an option itself depending on
		your browser settings).
        Table <ofx:reference target="table.user.ui.export.file"/> summarises these export options.
	</ofx:paragraph>

	
